main event: A round saucer-shaped object with red, blue, and white colors was observed in Gainesville, Florida, which disappeared straight up after 20 minutes.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 20 minutes,The object was visually confirmed to be round and saucer-shaped,The observation was received third hand from Jacksonville ARTCC,The object was believed to be a balloon based on reports from Tampa and Miami weather stations,The object was observed through binoculars.
witness description: third hand witness account from Jacksonville ARTCC
